17:05.816 --> 17:07.317
"Bersikap aneh di dekat orang asing."

17:07.359 --> 17:08.235
Oh, oke, ya.

17:14.241 --> 17:17.036
Oke. Sampai nanti.

17:24.334 --> 17:27.004
Sial.

17:51.328 --> 17:55.328
