21:35.002 --> 21:36.086
Ya.

21:36.128 --> 21:37.671
Ide bagus, Lucy.

21:37.713 --> 21:39.381
Kate, kau punya
nomor teleponnya mereka 'kan?

21:39.423 --> 21:40.299
Mm-hmm.

21:43.051 --> 21:43.969
Terima kasih.

21:45.262 --> 21:46.138
Oke.

21:46.805 --> 21:48.640
"Pesawat Para Cowok Seksi."

21:48.682 --> 21:50.017
Bagus. Berkelas.

21:53.312 --> 21:54.313
Hey, kamu yang nelpon.

21:55.480 --> 21:57.107
Hmm?
/ Ayo, Lucy-Lou.

21:58.025 --> 21:59.609
Ayolah, Lucy.
/ Hmm?

22:05.532 --> 22:06.491
Ayo.

22:13.874 --> 22:15.000
